ygData.messageBody:
Yes. Elven Wine Blessing. It seems they all are running to you, but in
reality, the Executioner in Qeynos <igloo.co.iup.edu/~vmjh/eq009.htm> just
doesn't like you come-ons.

Kapolokok

Also, the requirements for the spells are a given, but shouldn't mages get
some kind of profit for the time recouping mana after the spell is cast?
